f education and its role in achieving sustainable development. <br><br>As a leading UK provider of International Day of Education-related content, The Mandatory Training Group is proud to join the global community in celebrating this important day.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1391_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1392_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1393_">Definitions</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-concept-of-education-red-sneakers-school-sup-2023-11-27-05-01-03-utc.jpg?v=1710235988" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-concept-of-education-red-sneakers-school-sup-2023-11-27-05-01-03-utc.jpg?v=1710235988 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Empowering Minds: Celebrating International Day of Education - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Empowering Minds: Celebrating International Day of Education - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1395_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1396_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by valeriygoncharukphoto via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-1398_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-1399_"><b>International Day of Education</b> - Established by the United Nations General Assembly in 2018, the International Day of Education aims to promote the importance of education as a fundamental human right and a key driver of sustainable development.</li><li tabind